fields.object_repr: I Don't Give A Flock Socks
In Loving Memory Of Sleep Socks

fields.name: Flamingo Socks
fields.description: Flamingos: not just lawn ornaments. Rock these colorful socks with your shortest shorts for an outfit that screams “leisure,” or under your business casual work attire to make it clear you have Miami on the mind. Pair with an after work cocktail to make it feel like you aren’t already fed up with the week on Monday.

fields.name: Avocado Socks
fields.description: You must be from California. You add avocado to your sandwiches, smoothies, omelets and burritos, so why not add some to your wardrobe? Wear these creamy treat on your feet in either blue or brown fun socks, but remember one thing: they are the good kind of fat.

fields.name: Sushi Socks
fields.description: Constantly thinking about sushi? Look no further for colorful socks that will satisfy your mouth-watering cravings. These cool sushi socks provide everything you need to have an awesome dinner: chopsticks, rolls, sashimi, and even edamame. Bonus: no need to cash out on a crazy expensive meal when you can get your fix every time you open your sock drawer.

fields.name: Mmm... Donuts Socks
fields.description: If you have a Homer Simpson-esque obsession for colorful, sugary donuts… look no further than these awesome Socksmith pairs. Make this dessert a part of your morning routine alongside your daily cup of joe.

fields.name: Smart Ass Socks
fields.description: OK, genius. Can you figure out what these funny men’s socks mean? They feature a donkey graduate wearing a mortarboard and glasses. That’s right ... it’s a concept you’re really familiar with. It’s a smart ass! These hilariously irreverent socks are just right for the man who always has some kind of comeback ready. They're also a perfect gift for graduation!

fields.name: Not Drunk Socks
fields.description: Uh-oh! Something went wrong on these wildly funny men’s drinking socks. They say, “Are you drunk?” and have boxes for you to check “Yes” or “No.” But it looks like you missed the boxes altogether! That certainly does answer the question, though! These make a great gift idea for a friend or loved one who you enjoy tying one on with from time to time. Cheers!

fields.name: Classic Guitars Socks
fields.description: We’ve got a great pick for all you music lovers out there! These cool guitar socks for men feature an awesome pattern of all your favorite six-string classics, both acoustic and electric. They make a great gift idea for a guitar player or anyone who likes to rock out from time to time. Get ready for the solo!

fields.name: Tacos Socks
fields.description: These socks will give em’ something to taco bout. Dive feet first into your favorite meal featured on your favorite fun clothing item, in either purple or black. One thing we ask is that no matter how impossibly hungry you get, just please don’t try and eat these tacos.

fields.name: Pineapple Socks
fields.description: Dreaming of the beach, but not able to go? Then pull on these fun men’s food and drink socks! Their tropical vibe is sure to transport you to a sunny, ocean-front location. We love the sunglasses-wearing pineapples on these unique socks, especially since they appear to be sipping something tasty and tropical from a coconut. Mai tai, maybe? Pina colada? Mmm, the possibilities sound delicious!

fields.name: Helix Nebula Socks
fields.description: There are things out there on the edges of the cosmos that are just plain awesome, and the Helix Nebula might be right at the top of that list. These extremely cool outer space socks render that amazing celestial body in neon purple, orange, yellow and blue for a killer graphic effect that astronomy nuts will love!

fields.name: Purple Rooster Socks
fields.description: If you’re a chicken fan, we think the roosters on these fun socks will definitely help you give the birds a run for their money! These cool bird socks feature a pattern of colorful roosters against a bold purple background.

fields.name: Rainbow Stripe Paw Prints Socks
fields.description: Animal lovers will fall tail over paws for these fun, colorful paw print socks for men. They feature a gradient rainbow stripe in the background, with black paw prints that contrast and pop for a fun graphic appeal. Perfect for dog or cat owners, these stylish novelty socks look great on a walk with Fido or curled up on the couch with Sylvester.

fields.name: Great Wave Socks
fields.description: Arguably the most famous wood-block print in the world, Hokusai created the Great Wave as one piece in a series titled Thirty-six Views of Mount Fuji. Intended to focus on the colossal mountain in the background that most viewers consider an afterthought, don't let this traditional Japanese print fall to the wayside. By wearing these unique socks, tell the world to watch out — because you are ready to make waves.

fields.name: The Coolest Emperor Socks
fields.description: Get waddling in these cool penguin novelty socks for men! There are so many occasions where wearing these would make a great choice, but our favorite has to be the idea of any formal affair where you have to wear a tux. Do a little social commentary in your penguin suit and see how many laughs you get!

fields.name: Flag Socks
fields.description: These aren't your mother's American flag socks. Show how strongly you support your country by wearing this bold pair of red, white and blue socks whether it is the Fourth of July, or just an average work day. If you are proud to be an American, you know how to prove it with this cool pair that are as sweet as cherry pie.

fields.name: Broccoli Socks
fields.description: Broccoli crowns abound on these colorful socks for men. Did you know that broccoli is a great source of vitamin C and potassium? Broccoli is also delicious in salads and stir-fried dishes. Elevate this humble and often overlooked  veggie with these fun socks! They make great gifts for vegans, vegetarians and broccoli lovers (we know you’re out there)!

fields.name: Squid And Whale Socks
fields.description: You’ve been convinced since you read Jules Verne ... the giant squid is out there lurking in the depths! Now it’s in the depths of your shoes on these cool squid and whale socks for men, where the massive red-tentacled beast has caught the tail of a whale on your toes! We hope their struggle doesn’t trip you up! Great for ocean lovers and those who aren’t afraid of the deep sea ...

fields.name: Music Notes Socks
fields.description: Get moving through the day in these fun socks inspired by what moves you in your life: beautiful music. These cool men’s music note socks feature a black-and-gray pattern of different clefs and notes, making them a great choice for musicians or consummate appreciators. They’ll get your toes a’tapping!

fields.name: Squirrel Socks
fields.description: Squirrels fail to recover up to 74% of the nuts they bury, according to an actual study done by the University of Richmond in Virginia. And one of the causes is nut theft! (We swear we are not making this up.) The squirrel on these funny men’s socks is not messing around with his stash of acorns: He holds a stick and declares “My yard, my rules, my nuts!”

fields.name: Tacky Holiday Sweater Socks
fields.description: The ugly holiday sweaters are everywhere! They may be an assault on our eyes, but there's no escaping the trend. So let's embrace it and spread the cheer even farther — all the way down to your toes. Strap on these ugly sweater socks for your next Christmas or holiday party and let your inner tackiness shine bright!

fields.name: Dumpster Fire Socks | Men's
fields.description: “Greetings from…” they say, above a big green dumpster being consumed by fire. We’re not sure exactly when “dumpster fire” entered our lexicon, but we’re happy these funny men’s socks are taking full advantage. We especially love those flames across the toes!

fields.name: A Genius Composition Socks
fields.description: Your style will be note-perfect in these cool music socks for men! They feature a pattern like sheet music, with a staff running all over like a stripe and a complex array of musical notes. They’d make a great gift idea for any musician or music lover, from a band member to a frequent concert-goer.

fields.name: Shhh ... I'm Overthinking Socks
fields.description: If overthinking burned calories, we’d be dead! Well, the next time someone tries to tell you that you worry too much, show them the dazzling striped pattern on these funny women’s socks. If that doesn’t shut them up (because, you know, if they don't stop talking, how can you continue to over analyze?), then let them see the words at the top: “Shhhh ... I’m overthinking.”

fields.name: Wine And Coffee Socks
fields.description: We believe that there’s a time and a place for everything. These funny women’s food socks are here to reinforce that idea! They feature cups of coffee and glasses of wine. They also say “AM” and “PM,” although it seems to be a little ambiguous as to which goes with which. Looks like you’ll get to decide for yourself!

fields.name: Coffee Socks
fields.description: I’ll have a non-fat mocha frappuccino with two double shots, a splash of caramel, low cal whip, a douse of cinnamon, and oh- hold the caffeine, of course. If you prefer a simple coffee order over a spiel that will make your head spin, these back to basics coffee socks are for you. Covered in to go cups, mugs, and scattered coffee beans, feed a small part of your caffeine addiction with the help of these unique food socks, and enjoy the jolt of energy that comes with pouring yourself into this cool pair.

fields.name: Donut Socks
fields.description: Dunk your feet into this colorful pair of food socks and fall head over heels for the style… but do-nut say we didn’t warn you. Indulge in your favorite frosted treat without feeling your favorite jeans tighten. The sweet colors of these fun socks are just icing on the glazed donut!

fields.name: Tacos Socks
fields.description: Add some extra meat, tomato and lettuce into your diet with these awesomely colorful taco socks in either purple or black. No need to wait until Tuesday, feel free to indulge in your Mexican food cravings any day of the week.

fields.name: Sloth Stripe Socks
fields.description: The cutest (and slowest) creatures ever are just hanging out on these fun sloth socks! They feature a wide stripe print, with sloths just chilling on the stripes like they’re the branches of a favorite tree. If you see yourself in this lazy guy, slip into these cute animal socks and hit the couch with the remote control!

fields.name: Ocean Gets Me Socks
fields.description: You know who always waves back? The ocean. Pay tribute to your lifelong pal, the body of water that will always be there for you, and the saltiest friend ever with these funny women’s socks with the words “The ocean just gets me” on them. They’ve got a dreamy, sandy scene all over, too, perfect for lovers of the sea!

fields.name: A Genius Composition Socks
fields.description: Here comes the crescendo! Musicians and music lovers will swoon over these fun women’s crew socks adorned with sheet music. In stylish black and white, they’ve got a musical staff pattern covered with some complex composition of notes, perfect for women who grew up playing an instrument in band or orchestra or who simply want to show off how much they love music.

fields.name: Superpower Socks
fields.description: On those days when you feel ready to save the world, slip on these fun and empowering socks that say, “I’m a girl. What’s your superpower?” Splashes of red, orange and pink exploding from a star kinda remind us of how amazing women fill this sometimes-gray world with color and love every day. Get out there and make your life super!

fields.name: Starry Night Socks
fields.description: This painting needs no introduction. Van Gogh's famous Starry Night was painted from his view at the insane asylum, although he rightfully chose to omit the metal bars covering his window from the picture. If you are going insane over this masterpiece, rock the gorgeous painting on your unique art socks as an homage to the crazed artist himself.

fields.name: I Don't Give A Flock Socks
fields.description: It’s summertime, and you’ve got nowhere to be but standing right here on one foot! These funny flamingo socks feature the bright pink birds standing by signs that say, “I don’t give a flock,” perfect for those carefree days when you’re really exuding the tropical vibes. How dare someone ask you to be responsible when the weather is this nice?

fields.name: In Loving Memory Of Sleep Socks
fields.description: Are you feeling a little short on your beauty sleep? These funny women’s socks might help! They feature fluffy sheep just waiting to be counted and say, “In loving memory of sleep.” Sure, these cute socks would make a great gift for sleep-deprived new moms, but we think they’re also perfect for students, nurses, people who work at The Sock Drawer during the holidays ...

fields.name: Always Be A Unicorn Socks
fields.description: Some days, the magic that’s deep down inside every woman comes bubbling out all over! These funny unicorn socks are for the other days. They feature an image of a pretty pink unicorn and these wise words: “Always be yourself. Unless you can be a unicorn. Then always be a unicorn.” On the rough days, just pretend you’re a mythical, magical beast!

fields.name: When Pigs Fly Socks
fields.description: Sure I’ll believe these incredible socks are so cheap… when pigs fly. Oh, wait. Tell the world you intend to do the impossible by wearing these colorful animal socks wherever you go.

fields.name: Rainbow Stripe Paw Prints Socks
fields.description: Next time you’re heading out to pick up treats for your dog or a new catnip plant for your kitty, be sure to slip on these awesome and colorful paw print socks, too! Featuring a rainbow stripe background and tiny black animal prints, they’re an eye-catching way to show how much you love your furry friends!

fields.name: Elephant Love Socks
fields.description: There’s no denying it, your cool new pair of socks are the elephant in the room. You will fall in love with these elephants falling in love… wait, is that legal? Either way, treat yourself to this adorable pair and never forget what a great decision you made on this memorable day.

fields.name: Majestic Butterflies Socks
fields.description: We spy monarchs and swallowtails on these colorful and fun butterfly socks! What types can you spot? Perhaps one of the most gorgeously detailed styles we’ve ever had, these lovely crew socks look inspired by vintage nature posters and charts. We think they’d make a thoughtful gift for any gardener, nature lover or simply any woman with great taste.

fields.name: Screaming Goats Socks
fields.description: Is there any better way to let off a little steam than to watch one of those screaming goat videos online? No kidding (pun intended), you’ve just gotta laugh when you hear, “AAAAH!” Celebrate that bold, bleating love of life with these funny goat socks, perfect for animal lovers! They show everyone’s favorite farm animal mid-scream and offer a helpful phonetic lesson, too!

fields.name: Leopard Print Socks
fields.description: These wild animal-print socks for women can help you embrace your inner apex predator, or just add some wild flair to your wardrobe! The pattern matches a leopard’s spots — and did you know that those spots are actually called rosettes? Another fun fact: Leopards purr when they are happy. We wonder if they like to sit in boxes as well?

fields.name: Stop Talking Socks
fields.description: What a lovely, flowery, pretty pair of socks! Oh wait ... Well, you shut us up. Perfect for those moments when you need to send someone a not-so-subtle message in a subtle way, these fun and colorful "Stop Talking" socks from Blue Q get the point across beautifully. Can't we all just enjoy the pretty flowers in peace?

fields.name: Relaxed Rabbit Socks
fields.description: The fluffy rabbits on these cute women’s animal socks sure do look relaxed, hanging out in a bucolic field between pretty bunches of flowers. They remind us of spring, and they just might put a spring in your step, too! We just want to slip these bunny socks on and relax with a cup of tea and a copy of Beatrix Potter’s The Tale of Peter Rabbit. A great choice for Easter or year-round!
